OL,5, Finland's far-right finance minister,  
OL,6, Riikka Purra, has apologised for a     
OL,7, string of racist comments she posted 15
OL,8, years ago that have just come to light.
OL,10,FDescribing the posts as "stupid", she  
OL,11,Fsaid she was sorry for the harm and    
OL,12,Fresentment they had caused.            
OL,14,FMs Purra's Finns Party secured         
OL,15,Fhigh-profile cabinet posts in the new  
OL,16,Fgovernment of conservative Prime       
OL,17,FMinister Petteri Orpo.                 
OL,19,FBut in only three weeks it has been    
OL,20,Fbeset with accusations.                
